eorem] can be used to [OBJ:app_car_change_v_find_accel_question:calculate the components of a vector].","  <b>Vocabulary:</b>  [OBJ:expsec_d490:Pythagorean theorem], [OBJ:expsec_d490:right triangle]","  <b>STEM Skills:</b>  <b>    <br />  </b>1. Review [OBJ:expsec_a354:exponents].<b><br /></b>2. Review [OBJ:expsec_a356:PEMDAS].<b><br /></b>3. Review [OBJ:expsec_d466:vector components]."],"objNames":["wb_vector_magnitude","wb_math_pythag_theorem_defined"]}